Encode:

looks like the cam is a mix of 3 recordings, needed to be cut in pieces and every part needed adjusting perspective and ar differently
ended up with 3 parts with different resolution, from 720x288 up to 720x336, since i didnt want to crop 50 lines i added virtual borders
for the parts that didnt have the highest height, so no eggheads, no shrinked ones, and nothing cropped

added intro from a fan I.R thx m8, also appended the afterendcreditscene from another fan thx too
